# Cloudflare Pages redirects. Astro copies site/public/* to dist/, so this ships as
# dist/_redirects and Pages reads it at the edge.
#
# Canonical host = apex (solytus.com), matching astro.config.mjs `site`.
# Redirect www -> apex, preserving path + query (301 permanent).
# Requires BOTH solytus.com and www.solytus.com to be custom domains on the Pages
# project. (If you instead add a Cloudflare Redirect Rule, drop this to avoid overlap.)
https://www.solytus.com/* https://solytus.com/:splat 301
